title: My ranked experiences in platinum described in one "funny" video.

embed.description: Had to be made. All feedback is greatly appreciated! =)

body:
Hope you find this entertaining :D  {{champion:17}} 
_Let me know if there is something I can change!_

replies.body:
You hit platinum with those mechanics and actually bothering to walk past your river line? As nasus... vs teemo?

this is like bronze stupidity. 

No offense intended... this is just.... /facepalm

i have a friend who is platinum and he swears that nasus is a good teemo counter and should win the lane 100% of the time(and he wasn't talking about ap or lane pressure nasus) and as a former teemo main who has faced many a nasus and never lost lane and usually won the game (and having played nasus a little bit myself and being forced to go lane pressure builds before it was cool to hold off the teemos relentless harassment), I'm just like... how?

I mean this is a textbook teemo matchup. Without Jungler Babysitting, Nasus is just going to die over and over.

\> Playing AP Teemo.

It hurts as a Teemo Main.


Are you sure you are in Plat? I didnt hear any Autistic Screeching, Flaming, excess Spam Pinging, and general Know-it-all-ness in the video? Is this not a guarantee in plat over in EUW as it is in OCE?
